data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! PRIVATE POOL! MOTIVATED SELLER! GRANITE THROUGHT OUT Indulge in the epitome of Florida with this captivating property in the enchanting town of Davenport 25 mins away from the Disney Parks. A true oasis awaits, boasting a private pool that beckons relaxation and outdoor entertainment against the backdrop of the Florida sun. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence spans almost 2000 square feet, offering a spacious retreat for you and your loved ones. The heart of the home is adorned with granite countertops, seamlessly blending style and functionality in the kitchen and bathrooms. Immerse yourself in the perfect synergy of elegance and comfort as you navigate the thoughtfully designed living spaces. Whether you're basking in the sun-drenched pool area or enjoying the well-appointed interiors, this property is a sanctuary where every detail contributes to a life of leisure and sophistication. Don't miss the chance to make this haven in Davenport your own—a residence that redefines the art of living in the Sunshine State.
